---
title: Creamy Chicken, Mushroom & Rosemary Spaghetti with Cucumber Salad & Parmesan
description:  Button mushrooms work a treat with aromatic rosemary and a silky, Parmesan-spiked sauce in this crowd-pleasing
pasta dish. Serve with a sweet and peppery salad to cut the richness and meet your new go-to vegetarian dish.

*We’ve replaced the fettuccine in this recipe with spaghetti due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

